'''Menaka Lalwani''' ([[Hindi language|Hindi]]: '''मेनका लालवानी''' ''Mēnakā Lālavānī,'' born 3 November, is an [[Indian film|Indian]] [[actress]]. She is known for her appearances in Indian [[soap operas]].<ref>[http://cinema.pluz.in/movies/bollywood/29187/movie-photos/first-look-release/menka-lalwani.htm Menka lalwani - miss lovely first look launch function pictures - hindi movies<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref><ref>[http://www.glamsham.com/picture-gallery/nawazuddin-siddiqui-niharika-singh-promote-miss-lovely-in-a-college-gallery/event/12784/3/index.htm Menaka Lalwani at MISS LOVELY movie promotion - photo 3 : glamsham.com<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> Lalwani is a professional model, beauty pageant contestant and trained classical dancer.<ref>[http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/tv-news/menka-lalwani-talks-about-her-colourful-character-emotional-atyachaar Menka Lalwani talks about her "colourful" character in Emotional Atyachaar | Tellychakkar.com<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> She made her [[Hindi film]] debut with the 2013 film ''[[Miss Lovely]]''.<ref>{{youtube|id=LqMhqNlMTyQ|title= Menaka Lalwani in Miss Lovely}}</ref>

== Early life ==

Lalwani was born in [[Baroda]]. After graduating, she studied advertising and public relations.

== Television ==

* ''[[Akkad Bakkad Bambey Bo]]''
* ''[[Pavitra Rishtha]]'' as Shalini
* ''[[Baa Bahu Aur Baby]]'' as Rimjhim Thakkar (née Talwar)
* ''[[Love By Chance]]''
* ''[[Saraswatichandra (TV series)|Saraswatichandra]]'' as Aarti
* 
* ''[[Aahat (TV series)|Aahat]]''
* ''[[Byaah Hamari Bahoo Ka]]'' as Nupur (episode 4)
* ''[[CID (Indian TV series)|CID]]'' as Various Characters

== Filmography ==
*''[[Miss Lovely]]'' (Hindi) - 2013
*''[[Chudail Story]]'' (Hindi) - 2016 - as Ria

